'''Mango Groove''' ndi gulu la 11 la South African [[African popular music#Afropop|Afropop]] lomwe nyimbo zawo zimayimba nyimbo [[Pop music|zapamwamba]] ndi [[Township music|zamatauni]] -makamaka [[marabi]] ndi [[Kwela|kwala]] . 

Kuyambira pa maziko awo mu 1984, gululi latulutsa ma [[Studio album|studio]] asanu [[Studio album|ndi limodzi]] ndi maulendo ambiri.  Album yawo yatsopano, 2016's ''[[Faces to the Sun]]'' , inali zaka zoposa zinayi pakupanga.  

== Mbiri ==

=== Mapangidwe ===
Mango Groove yomwe inakhazikitsidwa ku [[Johannesburg]] mu 1984.  Amodzi mwa anthu anayi omwe adayambitsa mazikowa, John Leyden, Andy Craggs, ndi Bertrand Mouton-anali magulu achigwirizano omwe anali ndi "gulu lachizungu la" punk band "lotchedwa Pett Frog, pomwe anali ophunzira ku [[University of the Witwatersrand|yunivesite ya Witwatersrand]] .  Mu 1984 anyamata atatu adakumana ndi [[Jack Lerole|"Voice Voice" ya nyimbo yalala Jack Lerole]] ku nyumba ya Gallo Records ku Johannesburg.  Kumapeto kwa zaka za m'ma 1950, Lerole adatsogolera gulu la kula lotchedwa [[Elias and His Zig-Zag Jive Flutes|Elias ndi Zig Zig Zive za Jive]] .  John Leyden ankakondwera ndi jazz yaku South Africa nthawi ino.  Mbiri ya Lerole isanafike iye.  Iye ndi anyamata a Pett Frog anakambirana pamodzi, ndipo gulu lina linayamba kusintha. Dzina la gululi linapangidwa pa chakudya chamadzulo: pun pa mawu akuti "Munthu, go groove!". 

